This paper focuses on scene text recognition, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also mentions the use of supervised learning and neural networks, which are common techniques in natural language processing (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of synthetic and actual datasets, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR).
